This paper discusses anomaly detection techniques in deep learning, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), cybersecurity (cs.CR), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). However, since the focus is on deep learning, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG and cs.CV, followed by cs.AI, cs.CR, and cs.NE.
